{
  "stem": "9995.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And she took her hand and put on her husband, who was already dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And this is another picture which I carry with me, and I cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "She still had two sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Both of them survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Very beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "One, I think, married some English soldier after the war, and she moved to England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But she-- of course, I never told her what I have seen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "None of us told her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Because we knew that it would-- her mother was still alive also, that would devastate them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So I kept it in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And it's-- it was-- it was-- it still is a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was-- I don't remember her first name, but her name was, married name, Schpringood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew this family very well because my mother's brother, my uncle, when he was an apprentice, he was working for this guy, this engineer, father.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He taught him a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, he went to Argentina.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was in Buenos Aires and over there, and also in Paris, he learned his trade.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was his first guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I knew the family very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this young man, he was a very fine engineer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was in his 20s, and she was maybe 21 years old, and very, very beautiful girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And dying like this, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] If I would have been freed, at that time, I would have gone on a killing binge.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would have been killing all the Germans because it was-- I was so bitter and so frustrated that you have no idea.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It took me quite a while after the war to-- to become-- to-- to change into a human being.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I was completely different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
